- npm i fs-extra

- readJSON,writeJSON does stringify and parse too

# Video 3

- to upload files we need to use multer
  - npm i multer
- uploading files we use form-data
- create public folder in the root project
- in server.js:
  - import {join} from "path"
  - const publicFolderPath = join(process.cwd(), "./public")
  - server.use(express.static(publicFolderPath))
